  <description type="4">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Activities associated with this project include:

- Workshops value chain of specialty coffee and fair trade model
- Virtual Meetings of coffee with end customers
- Exchange practical experiences from &quot; farmer to farmer&quot;
- Technical support for 100 coffee farm families
- Selection of pilot farms postharvest
- Repair, maintenance and optimization of postharvest systems
- Community Meetings demonstrating methods of postharvest
- Tracking and monitoring the implementation of pilot postharvest</narrative>
  </description>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Goal: Coffee farmers produce a higher return on their harvests 

Direct Effect 1: Strengthening market and farmer linkages

Direct Effect 2: Strengthening and reproduction of agro-ecological coffee models

Direct Effect 3: Improving harvest and post-harvest processes.</narrative>
  </description>
